{
  "stem": "14251.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Elisabeth Abegg and say, what now?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She also tried to do some work from then on, some typing, some knitting, whatever she could to earn some extra money.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She helped the greengrocer lady.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She stayed there some of the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was able to do bookkeeping for her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But always the worry that you mustn't be seen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who is staying here?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Remember, that it is not like here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could have 20 people in your house if you feel like it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she got herself-- Elisabeth Abegg had done the best she could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother stayed in places and with people that she doesn't even recall, or how many.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She got herself a train ticket with money that she had and got the train ticket.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes they'd ask for ID and sometimes not as she was watching.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, she came up there and she-- I think she chatted up the train master who was selling the tickets and, therefore, got her ticket without her ID possibly and rode on the train supposedly by keeping the lock of the toilet on Unoccupied.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When the Gestapo would board the train, they wouldn't bother to look in there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And her seat would be empty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she rode a lot of the time on that train in the toilet with Unoccupied written there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she arrived and somehow appeared at the door months later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in the winter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I, I only remember saying-- and I don't even know why I said that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have no idea for the motivation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Is it true that my father's dead?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, I didn't say 'my father.' I said, 'Papi,' which is how you say.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's like daddy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she couldn't understand where I got that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know where I got that.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
